OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,7,Fbubbling up by afternoon. It will be
OL,8,Fwarm inland, but cooler along the east
OL,9,Fcoast where there will be an onshore
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with some sunny
OL,13,Fintervals. Some clear spells at first
OL,14,Ftonight but clouding over, some mist
OL,15,Fand low cloud in east, perhaps a light
OL,16,Fshower.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,19,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,20,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,21,Fwith some warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
