OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Perhaps some thundery showers
OL,8,Flater on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
